DADDIO
by
Christy Hall
OVER BLACK...
DING!
(LEFT OF SCREEN TEXT)
You fly today?
Then. That all too familiar “typewriter” clicking sound-
CLICK, CLICK, CLICK, CLICK, CLICK! BLOOP!
(RIGHT OF SCREEN TEXT)
Getting on plane now
Three little dots wave shades of gray on the LEFT OF
